ND--> <br><br>You could make a schedule where deposits and withdrawls could be made.  I dont know... just some thoughts.  <br><br>The downside to this is that those caretakers of those items would need to have regular access to the game and keep records on the levels of the items for quick reference.<br><br>Would be GREAT if a guildbank feature would be added when they provide the housing!!!!!!<br><br>Comments? <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=32353" target="_blank">Nummie Shinsplitter</a><BR>High Priest of Bristlebane <BR>Club FU <BR><BR>Saresh<BR>LvL 19 Infiltrator<BR>Numms<BR>LvL 10 Cleric<BR>Forgotten Truth  (Palomides)<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6B8E23><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ukrystl.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Krystl</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Duchess</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(2/21/02 7:30:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=925.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Thoughts on freeing up bank space.......</span><hr size=1> There is supposed to be a guild bank when we get a guild house...of course, who knows when that might be <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Krystl</i>, Albion Cleric of Palomides<br><font size="2"><b>Proud leader of The Forgotten Truth in DAoC<font size="1"><b><i>"Wait!  I'm lost!"</i></b></font> </p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 wi